{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":895,"text":"I'm an industrial engineer."},{"time":2631,"text":"The goal in my life has always been to make"},{"time":5428,"text":"more and more products"},{"time":6900,"text":"in the least amount of time and resources."},{"time":9410,"text":"While working at Toyota,"},{"time":10910,"text":"all I knew was how to make cars"},{"time":12875,"text":"until I met Dr. Akira Miyawaki,"},{"time":15328,"text":"who came to our factory to make a forest in it"},{"time":18511,"text":"in order to make it carbon-neutral."},{"time":21346,"text":"I was so fascinated"},{"time":23220,"text":"that I decided to learn this methodology"},{"time":25666,"text":"by joining his team as a volunteer."},{"time":28557,"text":"Soon, I started making a forest"},{"time":30379,"text":"in the backyard of my own house,"},{"time":32843,"text":"and this is how it looks after three years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36776,"text":"These forests,"},{"time":37910,"text":"compared to a conventional plantation,"},{"time":39960,"text":"grow 10 times faster,"},{"time":42382,"text":"they're 30 times more dense,"},{"time":44969,"text":"and 100 times more biodiverse."},{"time":48940,"text":"Within two years of having this forest in our backyard,"},{"time":51800,"text":"I could observe that the groundwater"},{"time":53744,"text":"didn't dry during summers,"},{"time":55623,"text":"the number of bird species I spotted in this area"},{"time":58480,"text":"doubled."},{"time":59650,"text":"Quality of air became better,"},{"time":61026,"text":"and we started harvesting seasonal fruits"},{"time":63587,"text":"growing effortlessly"},{"time":65319,"text":"right in the backyard of our house."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67930,"text":"I wanted to make more of these forests."},{"time":70247,"text":"I was so moved by these results"},{"time":71665,"text":"that I wanted to make these forests"},{"time":73689,"text":"with the same acumen with which we make cars"},{"time":76479,"text":"or write software or do any mainstream business,"},{"time":79899,"text":"so I founded a company"},{"time":81743,"text":"which is an end-to-end service provider"},{"time":83590,"text":"to create these native natural forests."},{"time":86935,"text":"But to make afforestation as a mainstream business"},{"time":90130,"text":"or an industry, we had to standardize"},{"time":92289,"text":"the process of forest-making."},{"time":94202,"text":"So we benchmarked the Toyota Production System"},{"time":96902,"text":"known for its quality and efficiency"},{"time":99916,"text":"for the process of forest-making."}]},{"cues":[{"time":101849,"text":"For an example, the core of TPS,"},{"time":104411,"text":"Toyota Production System, lies in heijunka,"},{"time":107751,"text":"which is making manufacturing"},{"time":109341,"text":"of different models of cars"},{"time":111790,"text":"on a single assembly line."},{"time":113881,"text":"We replaced these cars with trees,"},{"time":116727,"text":"using which now we can make multi-layered forests."},{"time":119650,"text":"These forests utilize 100 percent vertical space."},{"time":123218,"text":"They are so dense"},{"time":123967,"text":"that one can't even walk into them."},{"time":127516,"text":"For an example, we can make a 300-tree forest"},{"time":130750,"text":"in an area as small as the parking spaces of six cars."},{"time":135204,"text":"In order to reduce cost and our own carbon footprint,"},{"time":139284,"text":"we started utilizing local biomass"},{"time":141279,"text":"as soil amender and fertilizers."},{"time":144046,"text":"For example, coconut shells crushed in a machine"},{"time":146814,"text":"mixed with rice straw,"},{"time":150437,"text":"powder of rice husk mixed with organic manure"},{"time":154040,"text":"is finally dumped in soil on which"},{"time":156321,"text":"our forest is planted."},{"time":157658,"text":"Once planted, we use grass or rice straw"},{"time":160887,"text":"to cover the soil"},{"time":162619,"text":"so that all the water which goes into irrigation"},{"time":165173,"text":"doesn't get evaporated back into the atmosphere."},{"time":167866,"text":"And using these simple improvisations,"},{"time":169796,"text":"today we can make a forest"},{"time":171495,"text":"for a cost as low as the cost of an iPhone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":175361,"text":"Today, we are making forests in houses,"},{"time":177814,"text":"in schools, even in factories with the corporates."},{"time":181882,"text":"But that's not enough."},{"time":183860,"text":"There is a huge number of people"},{"time":185812,"text":"who want to take matters into their own hands."},{"time":188681,"text":"So we let it happen."},{"time":190545,"text":"Today, we are working on an Internet-based platform"},{"time":194785,"text":"where we are going to share our methodology"},{"time":197362,"text":"on an open source"},{"time":199319,"text":"using which anyone and everyone"},{"time":200770,"text":"can make their own forest"},{"time":202280,"text":"without our physical presence being there,"},{"time":204802,"text":"using our methodology."},{"time":206755,"text":"At the click of a button,"},{"time":208010,"text":"they can get to know all the native species"},{"time":209560,"text":"of their place."},{"time":211778,"text":"By installing a small hardware probe on site,"},{"time":215596,"text":"we can do remote soil testing,"},{"time":218296,"text":"using which we can give step-by-step instructions"},{"time":222101,"text":"on forest-making remotely."},{"time":225005,"text":"Also we can monitor the growth of this forest"},{"time":227917,"text":"without being on site."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231566,"text":"This methodology, I believe,"},{"time":233117,"text":"has a potential."},{"time":234862,"text":"By sharing, we can actually\nbring back our native forests."},{"time":237695,"text":"Now, when you go back home,"},{"time":239342,"text":"if you see a barren piece of land,"},{"time":241045,"text":"do remember that it can be a potential forest."}]},{"cues":[{"time":244638,"text":"Thank you very much. Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246828,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}